1
00:00:08,625 --> 00:00:11,375
- MY NAME'S NINA AND I'M A
PRETTY AVERAGE, ORDINARY GIRL.

2
00:00:11,458 --> 00:00:13,708
AT LEAST I WAS,
UNTIL ONE DAY.

3
00:00:13,791 --> 00:00:15,833
I ACCIDENTALLY
SWALLOWED SOMETHING

4
00:00:15,916 --> 00:00:16,958
CALLED THE CRYSTAL PEARL

5
00:00:17,041 --> 00:00:18,625
WHILE EATING
AT MY FAVORITE CAKE SHOP,

6
00:00:18,708 --> 00:00:21,041
AND MY LIFE
HASN'T BEEN THE SAME EVER SINCE.

7
00:00:21,125 --> 00:00:24,708
THIS PEARL IS AN IMPORTANT PART
OF AN OTHERWORLDLY SORCERY TEST.

8
00:00:24,791 --> 00:00:26,833
IT'S DROPPED RANDOMLY
INTO THE HUMAN WORLD,

9
00:00:26,916 --> 00:00:28,583
AND THE TEAM OF TWO EXAMINEES
WHO ARE ABLE

10
00:00:28,666 --> 00:00:30,750
TO TRACK IT DOWN FIRST
WILL PASS THE EXAMINATION

11
00:00:30,833 --> 00:00:33,041
AND BECOME
PROFESSIONAL SORCERERS.

12
00:00:33,125 --> 00:00:36,250
THEN GET THIS THING OUT OF ME!
- STOP CRYING.

13
00:00:36,333 --> 00:00:38,500
- YOU'RE JUST GONNA
HAVE TO PREPARE YOURSELF, ZERO.

14
00:00:38,583 --> 00:00:39,625
- HUH?

15
00:00:39,708 --> 00:00:40,958
- NOW THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY
TO DO THIS.

16
00:00:41,041 --> 00:00:43,041
LOOKS LIKE WE'LL HAVE TO
PROTECT HER ANY WAY WE CAN

17
00:00:43,125 --> 00:00:45,166
UNTIL THE DAY THE TEST IS OVER.

18
00:00:45,250 --> 00:00:47,250
WE'LL KEEP DILIGENT WATCH OVER
HER UNTIL THE MEDICINE IS READY

19
00:00:47,333 --> 00:00:49,458
AND WE CAN EXTRACT
THE CRYSTAL PEARL FROM HER BODY.

20
00:00:49,541 --> 00:00:51,666
WE'LL HAVE TO PROTECT THIS GIRL
WITH OUR VERY LIVES.

21
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:53,250
- ARE YOU SERIOUS?

22
00:00:53,333 --> 00:00:55,875
- SO YOU GUYS
ARE GONNA STAY HERE AND HELP ME?

23
00:00:55,958 --> 00:00:57,333
REALLY?

24
00:00:57,416 --> 00:00:59,375
JUST LIKE THE PRINCES
IN THE FAIRY TALE

25
00:00:59,458 --> 00:01:00,416
WHO BRAVELY FACE THEIR ENEMIES

26
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:02,208
NO MATTER HOW FEROCIOUS
THEY MAY BE,

27
00:01:02,291 --> 00:01:04,833
AND FIGHT TO THE BITTER END
FOR THE PEOPLE THAT THEY LOVE,

28
00:01:04,916 --> 00:01:06,916
THESE TWO
ARE HERE TO PROTECT ME.

29
00:02:38,250 --> 00:02:41,166
- ( alarm sounding )

30
00:02:41,250 --> 00:02:42,833
- ( yawning )

31
00:02:42,916 --> 00:02:45,416
I REALLY SLEPT LIKE A ROCK.
THAT'S WEIRD.

32
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:48,250
FOR SOME REASON, I FEEL LIKE I'M
FORGETTING SOMETHING IMPORTANT.

33
00:02:48,333 --> 00:02:49,541
OH, WELL.

34
00:02:49,625 --> 00:02:51,791
I BETTER HURRY UP
AND GET DRESSED.

35
00:02:55,208 --> 00:02:57,708
( shouting )

36
00:03:03,041 --> 00:03:06,833
NOOOOO!

37
00:03:12,958 --> 00:03:15,041
- Zero: JEEZ,
IT'S NOT A BIG DEAL.

38
00:03:15,125 --> 00:03:17,000
WHY CAN'T YOU GET USED
TO THE FACT

39
00:03:17,083 --> 00:03:19,041
THAT WE'RE YOUR ROOMMATES NOW?
- IT IS A BIG DEAL!

40
00:03:19,125 --> 00:03:21,041
I AM NOT ACCUSTOMED TO WAKING UP
IN THE MORNING

41
00:03:21,125 --> 00:03:23,083
AND FINDING
TWO HALF-NAKED MEN IN MY CLOSET.

42
00:03:23,166 --> 00:03:25,041
AND IF YOU WERE IN MY SHOES,
YOU WOULDN'T LIKE IT, EITHER.

43
00:03:25,125 --> 00:03:26,625
- I'M SORRY, NINA.

44
00:03:26,708 --> 00:03:28,791
WE'LL TRY TO USE
MORE DISCRETION IN THE FUTURE.

45
00:03:28,875 --> 00:03:31,083
- BUT SHE BARGED IN ON US
WITHOUT EVEN KNOCKING.

46
00:03:31,166 --> 00:03:32,583
- BUT IT'S MY ROOM, ZERO.

47
00:03:32,666 --> 00:03:33,625
I SHOULDN'T HAVE TO
KNOCK ON THE DOOR

48
00:03:33,708 --> 00:03:35,208
WHEN I WANT
TO OPEN MY OWN CLOSET.

49
00:03:35,291 --> 00:03:37,833
MAYBE YOU TWO SHOULD JUST SLEEP
IN THE CAR. THAT WOULD SAVE US

50
00:03:37,916 --> 00:03:40,166
FROM ANY MORE EMBARRASSING
SITUATIONS NOW, WOULDN'T IT?

51
00:03:40,250 --> 00:03:42,708
- YOU'RE RIGHT. BUT WE NEED TO
STAY AS CLOSE TO YOU AS POSSIBLE

52
00:03:42,791 --> 00:03:44,333
SO WE CAN PROTECT YOU.

53
00:03:44,416 --> 00:03:46,458
- Zura: NINA.
- THIS IS SO ANNOYING.

54
00:03:46,541 --> 00:03:48,458
- REMEMBER,
DON'T WANDER OFF AGAIN

55
00:03:48,541 --> 00:03:50,166
AND STICK CLOSE TO US
AT ALL TIMES.

56
00:03:50,250 --> 00:03:52,125
I WON'T LET YOU
OUT OF MY SIGHT

57
00:03:52,208 --> 00:03:53,250
'CAUSE I'M SICK
OF YOU CAUSING PROBLEMS.

58
00:03:53,333 --> 00:03:54,416
- BUT THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

59
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:56,416
BOYS CAN'T GO
TO MY P.E. CLASS.

60
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:59,083
- EITHER WE GO TO P.E. WITH YOU
OR YOU GET ATTACKED.

61
00:03:59,166 --> 00:04:00,833
GOT IT?
- YEAH, BUT I DON'T KNOW IF--

62
00:04:00,916 --> 00:04:02,916
- ( grunts )
- ZERO,

63
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:05,708
DON'T WALK AWAY WHILE WE'RE
TALKING. DO YOU HEAR ME?

64
00:04:08,208 --> 00:04:11,125
- ( girl crying )

65
00:04:11,208 --> 00:04:14,916
- ARE YOU OKAY?
CAN YOU WALK?

66
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,375
IF YOU CAN GET THE NURSE,

67
00:04:16,458 --> 00:04:18,083
SHE'LL CLEAN UP
THE SCRAPE FOR YOU.

68
00:04:18,166 --> 00:04:20,583
- BUT IT REALLY HURTS.
AHH!

69
00:04:20,666 --> 00:04:22,333
- WHAT HAPPENED?
- SHE FELL.

70
00:04:22,416 --> 00:04:24,875
- AW, DID YOU SCRAPE UP
YOUR KNEE?

71
00:04:24,958 --> 00:04:28,208
DOES IT STING?
- A LITTLE BIT.

72
00:04:28,291 --> 00:04:30,416
- LET'S GO.

73
00:04:33,250 --> 00:04:35,166
YOU FEEL BETTER?
- YES.

74
00:04:35,250 --> 00:04:37,041
- THIS SHOULD HELP
KEEP THE AREA CLEAN.

75
00:04:37,125 --> 00:04:39,458
OKAY, ALL DONE.
- ( giggles )

76
00:04:39,541 --> 00:04:41,750
- OH, YEAH.  HERE.

77
00:04:41,833 --> 00:04:43,708
- THANK YOU SO MUCH.

78
00:04:43,791 --> 00:04:45,916
NOW MY KNEE
DOESN'T EVEN HURT ANYMORE.

79
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,291
- ARE YOU GONNA BE OKAY?
- YEAH, I PROMISE.

80
00:04:48,375 --> 00:04:50,750
- JUST BE SURE TO HAVE YOUR
SCRAPE DISINFECTED

81
00:04:50,833 --> 00:04:51,583
WHEN YOU GET TO SCHOOL.

82
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:53,708
- THANK YOU!

83
00:04:53,791 --> 00:04:56,875
- MY PLEASURE, LITTLE GIRL.
JUST TRY TO BE MORE CAREFUL.

84
00:04:56,958 --> 00:04:59,916
YOU DON'T WANNA FALL DOWN
AND SCRAPE UP YOUR KNEE AGAIN.

85
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,125
- 'KAY!
- THAT WAS THOUGHTFUL OF YOU.

86
00:05:02,208 --> 00:05:06,208
YOU HAVE
A VERY SWEET DISPOSITION, NINA.

87
00:05:06,291 --> 00:05:09,458
- OH, ICHII.

88
00:05:12,625 --> 00:05:15,375
- I THINK YOU'RE A--

89
00:05:15,458 --> 00:05:19,041
A VERY SPECIAL PERSON, NINA.

90
00:05:19,125 --> 00:05:21,291
- THANK YOU.

91
00:05:21,375 --> 00:05:24,333
- Zero: HEY, SNAP OUT OF IT,
YOU TWO! WHAT'S THE MATTER?

92
00:05:24,416 --> 00:05:25,416
IF WE DON'T GET A MOVE ON,

93
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:26,916
THEN WE'RE ALL GONNA BE
LATE FOR SCHOOL!

94
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:30,625
STOP STARING AT EACH OTHER
AND GET OVER HERE IMMEDIATELY.

95
00:05:30,708 --> 00:05:34,250
LET'S GO!
- I'M COMING, ZERO.  SORRY.

96
00:05:34,333 --> 00:05:36,166
- ( chuckles )

97
00:05:36,250 --> 00:05:39,208
- JEEZ.

98
00:05:39,291 --> 00:05:41,250
- ( all squealing )

99
00:05:41,333 --> 00:05:43,166
- ZERO!
- ICHII!

100
00:05:46,583 --> 00:05:48,916
- THE RUMORS WERE TRUE.
YOU GUYS ARE REALLY HOT.

101
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,041
- WHERE ARE YOU FROM?
ARE YOU BROTHERS?

102
00:05:51,125 --> 00:05:52,708
- WHAT'S YOUR FAVORITE FOOD?

103
00:05:52,791 --> 00:05:55,291
- PLEASE PLEASE PLEASE
LET ME BE YOUR GIRLFRIEND.

104
00:05:55,375 --> 00:05:58,000
- Nina: HEY, NOW.
- GET OUT OF HERE, NINA!

105
00:05:58,083 --> 00:06:00,208
- WAIT A MINUTE!

106
00:06:00,291 --> 00:06:02,250
- THOSE GUYS ARE
ALWAYS SURROUNDED

107
00:06:02,333 --> 00:06:03,625
BY A GIANT GROUP OF GIRLS, HUH?

108
00:06:03,708 --> 00:06:07,125
- HATSUKA, YOUKA.
- BUT I GUESS THAT MAKES SENSE.

109
00:06:07,208 --> 00:06:09,375
YOU THREE HAVE BEEN THE TALK
OF THE SCHOOL LATELY.

110
00:06:09,458 --> 00:06:12,125
- Both: WE WANT TO KNOW,
ARE YOU THREE GOING OUT?

111
00:06:12,208 --> 00:06:14,458
TELL US.  HUH?

112
00:06:14,541 --> 00:06:16,875
- WELL, THAT'S--
- ( all screaming )

113
00:06:16,958 --> 00:06:21,500
- Girl: WAIT, DON'T GO.
- YOU DON'T HAVE TO RUN!

114
00:06:21,583 --> 00:06:24,375
- ( device beeping )
- HMM, IT'S CLOSE.

115
00:06:24,458 --> 00:06:26,083
- Machine: IT'S IN THE VICINITY.
- THE CRYSTAL PEARL.

116
00:06:26,166 --> 00:06:29,166
IT MUST BE HERE, LADY ROKKA.

117
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:33,541
- I DON'T CARE, GOU.
I JUST WANNA FIND ICHII.

118
00:06:33,625 --> 00:06:35,375
I MISS HIM.

119
00:06:35,458 --> 00:06:36,750
- I DON'T THINK THAT'S
A GOOD IDEA.

120
00:06:36,833 --> 00:06:37,583
- WHY NOT?

121
00:06:37,666 --> 00:06:39,000
- YOUR FATHER'S ALLOWED YOU

122
00:06:39,083 --> 00:06:41,291
TO TRAVEL TO THE HUMAN WORLD
FOR THE SOLE PURPOSE

123
00:06:41,375 --> 00:06:43,375
OF COMPLETING
THE FINAL SORCERY EXAM.

124
00:06:43,458 --> 00:06:45,791
AND NO MATTER WHAT PERSONAL
MATTERS YOU MAY BE DEALING WITH,

125
00:06:45,875 --> 00:06:47,458
WE MUST FIND THAT PEARL FIRST.

126
00:06:47,541 --> 00:06:50,333
- BUT YOU ARE MY PARTNER, RIGHT?
- NO.

127
00:06:50,416 --> 00:06:53,708
I'M MERELY YOUR HUMBLE SERVANT,
LADY ROKKA.

128
00:06:53,791 --> 00:06:55,625
- OOH!

129
00:06:55,708 --> 00:06:57,166
- I'M GETTING A STRONG READING
FROM THE FINDER.

130
00:06:57,250 --> 00:06:59,208
THE CRYSTAL PEARL
IS RIGHT OVER THERE.

131
00:06:59,291 --> 00:07:01,625
IT'S MOST LIKELY
INSIDE THAT BUILDING.

132
00:07:01,708 --> 00:07:04,625
- FINE, THEN LET'S GO.
I'VE ALREADY WASTED ENOUGH TIME

133
00:07:04,708 --> 00:07:07,291
AND THIS
IS GETTING REALLY ANNOYING.

134
00:07:09,791 --> 00:07:11,750
( squealing )

135
00:07:11,833 --> 00:07:15,083
ICHII, MY LOVE.
ICHII, ICHII!

136
00:07:15,166 --> 00:07:19,916
ICHII!  ICHII!
ICHII!  ICHII!

137
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,416
- IMAI.
- HERE.

138
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:23,500
- MY DARLING!

139
00:07:23,583 --> 00:07:25,208
I'VE BEEN LOOKING
FOR YOU EVERYWHERE

140
00:07:25,291 --> 00:07:27,333
AND NOW I'VE FOUND YOU!

141
00:07:27,416 --> 00:07:30,666
HOW I MISSED YOU.
MY ICHII!

142
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:33,166
HOW 'BOUT A KISS?

143
00:07:33,250 --> 00:07:35,375
- All:
ICHII, WHAT'RE YOU DOING?

144
00:07:35,458 --> 00:07:38,041
ICHII!  ICHII!

145
00:07:38,125 --> 00:07:40,166
- PLEASE TELL ME
THAT THIS IS ALL A BAD DREAM.

146
00:07:40,250 --> 00:07:42,333
- All: OH, HOW COULD YOU
POSSIBLY DO THIS TO US?

147
00:07:42,416 --> 00:07:44,291
PLEASE, STOP IT.

148
00:07:44,375 --> 00:07:46,125
YOU HAVE TO DO SOMETHING
ABOUT THIS RIGHT NOW, NINA.

149
00:07:46,208 --> 00:07:48,208
- YEAH, RIGHT.
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?

150
00:07:48,291 --> 00:07:50,541
- Ichii: ROKKA.
WHAT DO YOU THINK YOU'RE DOING?

151
00:07:50,625 --> 00:07:52,000
YOU'RE NOT ALONE, ARE YOU?

152
00:07:52,083 --> 00:07:54,416
- NO,
GOU IS TRAVELING WITH ME.

153
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:56,625
TO FOLLOW YOU
INTO THE HUMAN WORLD,

154
00:07:56,708 --> 00:07:59,666
WE BOTH BECAME EXAMINEES
FOR THE FINAL SORCERY EXAM.

155
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:02,500
- ARE YOU SERIOUS?
- LADY ROKKA.

156
00:08:02,583 --> 00:08:05,083
- GOU?
- LONG TIME NO SEE, ICHII.

157
00:08:05,166 --> 00:08:07,166
I APOLOGIZE,

158
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:09,958
BUT LADY ROKKA WAS EXTREMELY
EXCITED TO SEE YOU.

159
00:08:10,041 --> 00:08:12,000
WE SHOULD BE GOING NOW, ROKKA.

160
00:08:12,083 --> 00:08:14,500
ICHII SEEMS TO BE BUSY, AND IT'S
NOT NICE OF YOU TO BOTHER HIM.

161
00:08:14,583 --> 00:08:16,875
- NO!
ICHII DOESN'T MIND.

162
00:08:16,958 --> 00:08:18,791
I CAN STAY,
CAN'T I, MY LOVE?

163
00:08:18,875 --> 00:08:20,583
- HEY, NINA.
WHO IS THAT GIRL ANYWAY?

164
00:08:20,666 --> 00:08:22,375
- SHE'S NOT HIS GIRLFRIEND,
IS SHE?

165
00:08:22,458 --> 00:08:24,833
- NO, NOT QUITE.
HE'S MY FIANCE.

166
00:08:24,916 --> 00:08:26,833
- All:
DID YOU SAY HIS FIANCEE?

167
00:08:26,916 --> 00:08:28,875
- THAT ISN'T TRUE.
- I HOPE NOT.

168
00:08:28,958 --> 00:08:30,583
- WOW,
YOU SURE ARE A LADIES' MAN.

169
00:08:30,666 --> 00:08:32,500
- BOTH OF YOU SHUT UP.

170
00:08:32,583 --> 00:08:34,708
- HEY, ICHII MY LOVE, STOP
WASTING YOUR TIME WITH THEM.

171
00:08:34,791 --> 00:08:36,416
LET'S HURRY UP
AND GET BACK TO THE MAGIC WORLD

172
00:08:36,500 --> 00:08:39,041
SO WE CAN GET MARRIED
AND LIVE HAPPILY EVER AFTER.

173
00:08:39,125 --> 00:08:41,791
- ROKKA!  I'M SORRY
ABOUT ALL THIS COMMOTION, NINA.

174
00:08:41,875 --> 00:08:43,583
I'LL GET THEM OUT OF HERE
AS SOON AS I CAN.

175
00:08:43,666 --> 00:08:45,375
- OH, DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT,
ICHII.

176
00:08:45,458 --> 00:08:48,583
- AND JUST WHAT DO YOU WANT?
YOU MAKING MOVES ON MY MAN?

177
00:08:48,666 --> 00:08:50,791
IF SO, THEN YOU'RE
IN BIG TROUBLE, MISSY.

178
00:08:50,875 --> 00:08:51,791
- HUH?

179
00:08:51,875 --> 00:08:53,666
IT'S-- IT'S NOT LIKE THAT.
UH...

180
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:55,541
- LEAVE HER ALONE, ROKKA.
- HUH?

181
00:08:55,625 --> 00:08:57,583
- SHE'S AN IMPORTANT PERSON
TO ME.

182
00:08:57,666 --> 00:08:58,916
- WAIT A MINUTE.

183
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:03,375
SHE'S MORE IMPORTANT
THAN ME?!

184
00:09:03,458 --> 00:09:06,000
OH!  THAT'S IT!

185
00:09:06,083 --> 00:09:08,291
YOU'D BETTER STAY
AWAY FROM HIM.

186
00:09:08,375 --> 00:09:10,583
I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHAT HE SEES
IN YOUR FLAT CHEST.

187
00:09:10,666 --> 00:09:13,375
NO BOOBS!
NO BOOBS!

188
00:09:13,458 --> 00:09:16,625
- YOU BETTER SHUT YOUR--
- STOP IT RIGHT NOW.

189
00:09:16,708 --> 00:09:19,375
I DON'T WANT YOU SAYING ANY MORE
RUDE THINGS TO MY FRIEND.

190
00:09:19,458 --> 00:09:22,875
- BUT ICHII, SHE WAS TRYING
TO STEAL YOU FROM ME.

191
00:09:22,958 --> 00:09:25,875
YOU BELONG TO ME, ICHII,
ME ALONE,

192
00:09:25,958 --> 00:09:28,416
AND I WON'T LET ANYONE
TAKE YOU AWAY FROM ME, MY LOVE.

193
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:30,250
I JUST CAN'T STAND
TO BE WITHOUT YOU

194
00:09:30,333 --> 00:09:32,916
FOR EVEN ONE MINUTE LONGER!

195
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,625
- WAIT, LADY ROKKA!

196
00:09:38,125 --> 00:09:39,583
TAKE THIS.

197
00:09:39,666 --> 00:09:41,541
AND IF IT'S NOT ENOUGH,
SEND ME THE BILL.

198
00:09:41,625 --> 00:09:45,666
I'M SORRY FOR THE DISTURBANCE,
EVERYONE.

199
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:49,375
ROKKA, DON'T RUN OFF!
WAIT FOR ME.

200
00:09:49,458 --> 00:09:51,375
- WHERE IN THE WORLD
DID THEY COME FROM?

201
00:09:51,458 --> 00:09:53,291
- Ichii: THEY'RE NUMBERS 005
AND 006.

202
00:09:55,625 --> 00:09:58,125
ROKKA IS A PERSISTENT ONE,
TO SAY THE LEAST.

203
00:09:58,208 --> 00:10:01,458
AND GOU IS HER BUTLER.
HE CARRIES OUT HER EVERY WISH.

204
00:10:01,541 --> 00:10:03,250
AND, WELL,

205
00:10:03,333 --> 00:10:06,125
NOW I THINK THEY'VE GOT THEIR
SIGHTS SET ON YOU, NINA.

206
00:10:06,208 --> 00:10:08,333
- OH, NO!
- BUT DON'T WORRY.

207
00:10:08,416 --> 00:10:11,083
YOU HAVE MY WORD THAT WE WON'T
LET ANY HARM COME TO YOU.

208
00:10:11,166 --> 00:10:12,791
- NO MATTER
WHAT WE'RE UP AGAINST,

209
00:10:12,875 --> 00:10:15,041
WE PROMISE WE'LL PROTECT YOU.
YOU'RE SAFE.

210
00:10:15,125 --> 00:10:18,375
- OH, YEAH.  HEH.
I GOT THIS FOR YOU.

211
00:10:18,458 --> 00:10:20,333
- FOR ME?
- YEP.

212
00:10:20,416 --> 00:10:23,166
I GOT YOU THIS LOLLIPOP BECAUSE
I THOUGHT IT FIT YOUR IMAGE.

213
00:10:23,250 --> 00:10:27,375
IT'S CUTE, LIKE YOU ARE.
- YOU THINK I'M CUTE?

214
00:10:27,458 --> 00:10:30,500
- OH, YES, NINA.

215
00:10:30,583 --> 00:10:34,708
I THINK
YOU'RE VERY VERY CUTE.

216
00:10:36,125 --> 00:10:37,958
- OH, THANK YOU.

217
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:42,708
BUT...

218
00:10:42,791 --> 00:10:44,375
WHY DID YOU DO IT?

219
00:10:44,458 --> 00:10:47,000
WHY DID YOU LET THAT MEAN GIRL
ROKKA KISS YOU?

220
00:10:47,083 --> 00:10:48,791
