- YOU DID THAT FOR ME?

441
00:21:24,541 --> 00:21:27,125
- WHY DO YOU CARE ABOUT
A LITTLE GIRL LIKE HER, ICHII?

442
00:21:27,208 --> 00:21:29,541
I'M A MUCH MUCH
MUCH BETTER WOMAN THAN SHE IS

443
00:21:29,625 --> 00:21:31,958
AND I CARE ABOUT YOU
MORE THAN SHE EVER WILL.

444
00:21:32,041 --> 00:21:34,416
WHY WON'T YOU COME BACK HOME
AND MARRY ME?

445
00:21:34,500 --> 00:21:37,833
- BECAUSE
I CAN'T LEAVE NINA NOW.

446
00:21:37,916 --> 00:21:39,375
I'VE SWORN TO PROTECT HER.

447
00:21:39,458 --> 00:21:42,791
- I SEE.
SO THAT'S HOW IT'S GONNA BE.

448
00:21:42,875 --> 00:21:45,000
I HOPE YOU KNOW

449
00:21:45,083 --> 00:21:48,291
THAT YOU'RE BREAKING MY HEART!

450
00:21:48,375 --> 00:21:51,291
( crying )
- SHE'S REALLY A LITTLE GIRL?!

451
00:21:51,375 --> 00:21:52,833
- YEAH, THAT'S RIGHT.

452
00:21:52,916 --> 00:21:54,791
LADY ROKKA HERE
IS REALLY ONLY FIVE YEARS OLD.

453
00:21:54,875 --> 00:21:56,666
- OF COURSE.

454
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:58,833
THAT'S WHY ICHII WASN'T FAZED
WHEN SHE KISSED HIM.

455
00:21:58,916 --> 00:22:03,458
AND WHY HE DIDN'T GET ANGRY
WHEN HE TURNED ROKKA AWAY.

456
00:22:03,541 --> 00:22:05,166
- I THOUGHT
I COULD GET ICHII BACK

457
00:22:05,250 --> 00:22:06,833
IF I TURNED YOU
INTO A LITTLE GIRL.

458
00:22:06,916 --> 00:22:08,625
I THOUGHT WITH YOU
OUT OF THE PICTURE,

459
00:22:08,708 --> 00:22:11,125
HE WOULD COME HOME WITH ME.
( crying )

460
00:22:11,208 --> 00:22:13,375
- SORRY, ROKKA.

461
00:22:13,458 --> 00:22:15,875
BUT I CAN'T GO BACK
TO THE MAGIC WORLD RIGHT NOW.

462
00:22:15,958 --> 00:22:17,708
I HAVE TO STAY HERE
AND PROTECT NINA

463
00:22:17,791 --> 00:22:19,958
AND MAKE MY DREAM COME TRUE.
YOU UNDERSTAND, RIGHT?

464
00:22:20,041 --> 00:22:22,041
- NO NO NO.
I WANNA BE WITH YOU, ICHII.

465
00:22:22,125 --> 00:22:24,500
I WANNA BE WITH YOU FOREVER
AND EVER AND EVER AND EVER!

466
00:22:24,583 --> 00:22:27,250
- NOW NOW,
WE REALLY SHOULD GET BACK.

467
00:22:27,333 --> 00:22:30,208
IF YOU LIKE, I'LL MAKE YOU A BIG
BOWL OF YOUR FAVORITE STEW.

468
00:22:30,291 --> 00:22:31,833
- ROKKA.

469
00:22:31,916 --> 00:22:33,416
- NO, I DON'T WANNA
GO WITHOUT YOU.

470
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:35,375
I'LL NEVER GIVE UP ON YOU,
ICHII.

471
00:22:35,458 --> 00:22:37,458
I KNOW THAT WE'RE MEANT
TO BE TOGETHER FOREVER AND EVER

472
00:22:37,541 --> 00:22:40,625
AND I DON'T WANNA LEAVE YOU!
- GOODBYE, EVERYONE.

473
00:22:40,708 --> 00:22:42,875
- NO, I DON'T WANT TO!

474
00:22:42,958 --> 00:22:45,833
GOODBYE, ICHII!
- TILL WE MEET AGAIN.

475
00:22:45,916 --> 00:22:48,291
- FINALLY.
- SWEET GIRLFRIEND, ICHII.

476
00:22:48,375 --> 00:22:52,333
- HEY.
- ( all laughing )

477
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:02,791
- HEY, ICHII,
MIND IF I ASK YOU SOMETHING?

478
00:23:02,875 --> 00:23:04,541
- NO.  WHAT IS IT?

479
00:23:04,625 --> 00:23:07,291
- HOW EXACTLY DID YOU KNOW
WHICH BABY WAS THE REAL ME?

480
00:23:07,375 --> 00:23:09,333
HATSUKA AND YOUKA
COULDN'T TELL,

481
00:23:09,416 --> 00:23:12,208
AND THEY'VE KNOWN ME LONGER
THAN YOU HAVE.

482
00:23:12,291 --> 00:23:13,625
- IT WAS EASY.

483
00:23:13,708 --> 00:23:15,708
THERE WERE A LOT OF BABIES
THAT LOOKED JUST LIKE YOU.

484
00:23:15,791 --> 00:23:18,458
BUT YOU WERE THE ONLY ONE
WHO TRIED TO SAVE ZURA.

485
00:23:18,541 --> 00:23:22,125
YOU'RE REALLY SWEET, NINA.

486
00:23:22,208 --> 00:23:25,791
- HUH?
- YOU'RE A VERY SPECIAL GIRL.

487
00:23:31,458 --> 00:23:33,375
- WHAT ARE YOU TWO DOING?
LET'S GET GOING.

488
00:23:33,458 --> 00:23:35,291
I'M HUNGRY
AND TIRED OF WAITING ON YOU.

489
00:23:35,375 --> 00:23:36,208
- OH, ZERO.

490
00:23:36,291 --> 00:23:38,041
- NO, HE'S RIGHT. READY TO GO?

491
00:23:38,125 --> 00:23:40,041
- ( both laughing )

492
00:23:40,125 --> 00:23:42,000
- Zero: HURRY UP.
I'M STARVING.

493
00:23:42,083 --> 00:23:45,958
- YOU'RE ALWAYS SO SWEET, NINA,
TO EVERYONE AND EVERYTHING.

494
00:25:17,041 --> 00:25:18,750
- San: DID YOU KNOW THAT NINA
AND THE OTHERS

495
00:25:18,833 --> 00:25:20,458
ARE PLANNING A TRIP
TO THE HOT SPRINGS?

496
00:25:20,541 --> 00:25:22,375
- Forte: REALLY?
THAT'S OUR CHANCE.

497
00:25:22,458 --> 00:25:24,250
- Rokka: DID YOU HEAR THAT?
LET'S GO TOO.

498
00:25:24,333 --> 00:25:26,416
- Gou: SO WE CAN ATTEMPT
TO OBTAIN THE CRYSTAL PEARL

499
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:28,708
WHILE THEY AREN'T LOOKING?
- NO, I'VE ALREADY TOLD YOU,

500
00:25:28,791 --> 00:25:30,625
I DON'T CARE ABOUT THE PEARL.

501
00:25:30,708 --> 00:25:32,708
I'VE GOTTA STOP THAT LITTLE
MONSTER FROM GETTING MY MAN.

502
00:25:32,791 --> 00:25:34,500
- LADY ROKKA,
PLEASE CALM DOWN.

503
00:25:34,583 --> 00:25:36,541
- ICHII, MY LOVE,
I'M COMING FOR YOU!

504
00:25:36,625 --> 00:25:39,291
- Nina: NEXT TIME
ON "SAVE ME LOLLIPOP"...

505
00:25:41,875 --> 00:25:45,583
HUH?  WAIT A MINUTE.
WHAT DID I JUST SAY?

